# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# INSTAGRAM ANALYZER — ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES EXAMPLE
# Copy this file to .env and replace with your actual keys
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

META_APP_ID=your_app_id_from_meta_developer_console
META_APP_SECRET=your_app_secret_from_meta_developer_console
META_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_long_lived_access_token_from_graph_api_explorer
INSTAGRAM_BUSINESS_ACCOUNT_ID=your_instagram_business_account_id

ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your_anthropic_api_key_from_console

PORT=3001
NODE_ENV=development
CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173

CACHE_TTL_MINUTES=60
DB_PATH=./server/db/cache.sqlite

RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS=900000
RATE_LIMIT_MAX_REQUESTS=100

GRAPH_API_VERSION=v21.0
GRAPH_API_BASE_URL=https://graph.facebook.com
